profile:
We have been providing the Fraser Valley and Lower Mainland with commercial and residential tree services as Pro Tree Services since 1999.  We have almost 30 years of experience on the team.  We have been BBB accredited since 2004, we are Worksafe current with a great record, and are fully insured.

Whether you need a tree removed for aesthetic or safety reasons, our crew has the tools and experience to do the work safely.

We are equipped with a boom truck capable of reaching up to 60 feet; our crew provides emergency and general tree care maintenance services focused on tree health and sustainability.  We are available for emergency tree services 24 hours a day/7 days a week.
